{{vgname|赛车总动员|en=Cars}}是一款根据2006年同名电影《[[汽車總動員|汽車總動員]]》所制作的开放世界[[竞速类游戏|竞速类游戏]]。本游戏由[[THQ|THQ]]在[[Game_Boy_Advance|Game Boy Advance]]、[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]、[[GameCube|GameCube]]、[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]、[[PlayStation_Portable|PlayStation Portable]]、[[Xbox_(遊戲機)|Xbox]]、[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]和[[Wii|Wii]]发行。<ref>[http://www.carsvideogame.com/original/ Cars: The Videogame] {{Wayback|url=http://www.carsvideogame.com/original/ |date=20101204092657 }}. Carsvideogame.com. Retrieved on 2010-12-10.</ref>

游戏设定在一个虚拟城市Radiator Springs。玩家需要完成50场比赛，来帮助Lightning McQueen赢得Piston杯。

《赛车总动员》收到正面评价。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]给予Xbox 360、PlayStation 3和Wii版本7/10的分数。给予GameCube和Xbox版本7.6/10的分数，给予PSP版本7.4/10的分数。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamespot.com/cars-the-movie/reviews/ | title = GameSpot Review | date = 2011-12-10 | accessdate = 2016-02-29 | archive-date = 2014-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140306015927/http://www.gamespot.com/cars-the-movie/reviews/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

